# ==============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS — Carizmi Community Platform
# ==============================================================================
#
# This file defines code ownership rules. When a PR modifies files matching
# a pattern below, the listed owner(s) are AUTOMATICALLY requested as reviewers.
#
# Combined with the Branch Protection rule "Require review from Code Owners",
# PRs CANNOT be merged without approval from the designated owner.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Global: Default owner for ALL files (catch-all)
# Any file not matched by a more specific rule below requires this owner's review
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*                                               @mujib-adm

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CI/CD & Infrastructure (CRITICAL — controls what runs in production)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.github/                                        @mujib-adm
docker-compose*.yml                             @mujib-adm
backend/Dockerfile                              @mujib-adm
frontend/Dockerfile                             @mujib-adm
